  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GenericFeature
    Basic interface for a feature object
    GmlIdGenerator<T>
    Interface for GML ID generators
    IFeature
    Simple interface for feature objects
    IFeatureCollection  
    IFeatureStaxBindings<T extends IFeature>
    Interface for StAX bindings of specific feature types
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtensibleFeatureImpl
    Base class for implementing custom features based on application schemas.
    Subclasses typically add new fields along with corresponding getters and setters and must override #appendProperties() to expose these properties in a generic way.
    FeatureRef<T extends IFeature>
    Wrapper class for use when an IFeature object is or can be included by reference.
    GenericFeatureImpl
    Generic implementation of a GML feature.
    GenericTemporalFeatureImpl  
    GeoJsonBindings
    GeoJSON bindings using Gson JsonWriter/JsonReader.
    This class is NOT threadsafe.
    GMLStaxBindings
    Helper wrapping the auto-generated GML StAX bindings
    GMLUnitReader
    TODO GMLUnitReader type description
    GMLUtils
    Utility methods to read/write GML documents.
    JTSUtils
    Utility methods for implementing JTS based GML geometries
    SequentialIdGenerator<T>
    Implementation of GML ID generator that just creates numerical IDs in sequence, prefixed by a configurable string.
